Quote:  Only the alpine shield fern (<i>Polystichum cystostegia</i>), bladder fern (<i>Cystopteris tasmanica</i>), mountain kiokio (<i>Blechnum montanum</i>), thousand-leaved fern (<i>Hypolepis millefolium</i>), finger ferns (<i>Grammitis poeppigiana</i> and <i>G. givenii</i>), one filmy fern (<i>Hymenophyllum villosum</i>) and two clubmosses (<i>Huperzia australiana</i> and <i>Lycopodium fastigiatum</i>) are found primarily in this habitat
